project_descr: Supporting Community Development in the Horn of Africa through Food Security (Djibouti, Somalia, Ethiopia)

outputs.output_descr: Supporting Community Development in the Horn of Africa through Food Security in Djibouti. Support to IGAD strategy on food security.

Three food/cash/voucher interventions achieved and certified as completed in each of the target countries.  At least five micro-scale projects developed in each of the target countries.  Ten  local communities assisted in water management initiatives in each of the target countries.
